164
0:08:55.076,000 --> 0:08:57,000
Tracie Keesee: Now, that's better, alright.

165
0:08:57.109,000 --> 0:09:,000
The first one: There's no more wallowing in the why.

166
0:09:00.982,000 --> 0:09:01,000
