170
0:09:15.97,000 --> 0:09:19,000
and we must make sure we never go back to a place where we cannot move forward.

171
0:09:21.82,000 --> 0:09:22,000
And number three:

172
0:09:23.955,000 --> 0:09:25,000
We must also make sure

173
0:09:26.304,000 --> 0:09:31,000
that truth and telling facts is painful.

174
0:09:32.48,000 --> 0:09:36,000
But we also know that no action is no longer acceptable.

175
0:09:37.274,000 --> 0:09:38,000
And agree?

176
0:09:38.836,000 --> 0:09:39,000
Audience: Yes.

